          exercitationem. Nobis, hic. Praesentium provident eaque, dolorum
          dolore rem ullam id delectus quae?
        </p>
        <div class="socialmedia">
          <div class="socialitem">
            <a href="https://tr-tr.facebook.com"
              ><img
                src="https://img.icons8.com/plasticine/48/000000/facebook-new.png"
            /></a>
          </div>
          <div class="socialitem">
            <a href="https://twitter.com"
              ><img
                src="https://img.icons8.com/doodle/48/000000/twitter--v1.png"
            /></a>
          </div>
          <div class="socialitem">
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/?hl=tr"
              ><img
                src="https://img.icons8.com/plasticine/50/000000/instagram-new.png"
            /></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <ul class="footerright">
        <li>
          <h2>Kurumsal</h2>
          <ul class="box">
            <li><a href="/aboutus">Hakkımızda</a></li>
            <li><a href="/privacypolicy">Gizlilik Politikası</a></li>
            <li><a href="/Useragreement">Kullanıcı Sözleşmesi</a></li>
